{"tid":374950,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"東亞人算唔算係白皮膚?","createTime":"2017-08-26T06:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T23:30:51.000Z","uid":61728,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ec06b5fb4b0a5c59907075a31406138c17fb134","tid":374950,"uid":61728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:57:36.000Z","msg":"唔係想講白皮膚係唔係優越d<br />\n只係純粹好好奇，<br />\n外國人已經唔會再用「黃種人」依個字，一黎依個字係有歧視成份，二黎都真係發現東亞人並唔係「黃皮膚」<br />\n<br />\n再者東亞人膚色又的確係同大部份白人一樣色<br />\n好多時你遮左個樣，其實係唔會分得出邊個係白人邊個係東亞人<br />\n當然有d白人既種係白到紅皮膚，但大部份都係同我地一樣色<br />\n<br />\n我又睇到wiki有一頁係講light skin<br />\n都係講到明只有東亞人同白人係屬於light skin<br />\n甚至有d西方人都會將東亞人當成係白皮膚既一種<br />\n<br />\n好好奇，除左我地講自己係「黃皮膚」外<br />\n其實外國人係唔係將東亞人當成白皮膚? (唔係當成白人，只係白皮膚)"},{"pid":"ab62e3479c8f1e159cd877ab62fe6c086110d392","tid":374950,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:59:49.000Z","msg":"所謂嘅膚色，背後係指種族"},{"pid":"b53497af3c6cb232663b127ff7120947839936dd","tid":374950,"uid":61728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所謂嘅膚色，背後係指種族</blockquote><br />\n當然啦<br />\n但如果單純講膚色，我的確唔係太覺得東亞人同白人有太大分別<br />\n最白既一定係白人，但係兩者膚色重疊既位好多、好明顯<br />\n正如正常一個白人/東亞人唔會同南亞人/黑人有膚色重疊"},{"pid":"a0137f91520a1eeeb71228b0ecfb3d0e6809f2d6","tid":374950,"uid":61728,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所謂嘅膚色，背後係指種族</blockquote><br />\n當然啦<br />\n但如果單純講膚色，我的確唔係太覺得東亞人同白人有太大分別<br />\n最白既一定係白人，但係兩者膚色重疊既位好多、好明顯<br />\n正如正常一個白人/東亞人唔會同南亞人/黑人有膚色重疊</blockquote><br />\n一個黑人白過白人會覺得好神秘、冇可能發生<br />\n一個南亞人好似東亞人咁白都好少見、都冇咩可能發生<br />\n但從來唔會有人覺得一個東亞人白過白人係好少見既事"},{"pid":"27b2ad38d6ba60bfd8f66dc04106f425f231122a","tid":374950,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"我地隻色 同意大利法國人好似"},{"pid":"0a9a98d955f3b711eabe85ee090b7e5b69ac38da","tid":374950,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"膚色其實有冇一個學術上/醫學上嘅分類"},{"pid":"5e42d68482d46ba1b02feba06038340979737b06","tid":374950,"uid":20815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"唔算，因為有牛肺"},{"pid":"fce511c2d66f373ada0b0a967b4ef18c3c737de0","tid":374950,"uid":61728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地隻色 同意大利法國人好似</blockquote><br />\n北歐人真係白到紅色<br />\n但我見中歐人隻色真係同我地差不多<br />\n南歐就更加係黑過我地好多"},{"pid":"769b620e8c31aa61e205ce5481a52e2e668fee52","tid":374950,"uid":61728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>膚色其實有冇一個學術上/醫學上嘅分類</blockquote><br />\n冇分類但事實上又真係有分別<br />\n如果膚色0係最白10係最黑<br />\n可能白人係0-3<br />\n東亞人係1-4<br />\n南亞人係4-7<br />\n黑人係7-10咁"},{"pid":"864fa4a5f06cf13c0bed7ba74e37e87aa1584605","tid":374950,"uid":61728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔算，因為有牛肺</blockquote><br />\n依度我又想問多一個問題<br />\n如果毛髮顏色同黑色素有關<br />\n咁又點解我地係黑眼黑髮?<br />\n觀察上我諗的確係冇人會反對白人一定白過我地<br />\n點解有D金髮藍眼既白人就算冇曬黑，都係同我地一樣咁既色?<br />\n但我地從來唔會有D好白既人係金髮藍眼?"},{"pid":"809f7e6d67bb5b76b8f99b7ff81a61190e31f25d","tid":374950,"uid":17530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:47:38.000Z","msg":"東亞狗就係東亞狗<br />\n皮膚白唔會令你種族優越啲"},{"pid":"38854d4b853078f0310023a597fe61617f0cc603","tid":374950,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:51:28.000Z","msg":"以前傳教失敗先改口黃皮膚<br />\n由一開始就係白皮膚"},{"pid":"cd503afef6a5857a7a3e577137f64b15ad013f54","tid":374950,"uid":61728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東亞狗就係東亞狗<br />\n皮膚白唔會令你種族優越啲</blockquote><br />\n咪一早講左唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但自己自稱黃皮膚咪仲歧視自己<br />\n人地叫我地黃皮膚係有歧視成份，依家要改正返都唔得? 邊個先係東亞狗?"},{"pid":"8f2146be7e908a82faefccd18f29cff3378f5bbf","tid":374950,"uid":40216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:24:15.000Z","msg":"The&nbsp;stratum corneum&nbsp;of Mongoloid skin contains lots of&nbsp;keratin, African and Melanesian skin has low amounts of keratin, and European skin lacks keratin.<br />\n<br />\nMongoloids have &quot;yellowish skin&quot;, because the&nbsp;stratum corneum&nbsp;of Mongoloid skin contains lots of &quot;disks of&nbsp;keratin&quot;"},{"pid":"1c7704dba60c4b02cce4d847b372a2acddbd09ea","tid":374950,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"屌，我都覺左好多年<br />\n不過呢個標準都係班鬼佬整出黎，背後既歧視意味好明顯<br />\n事實我地同南亞個班D色真係差好遠"},{"pid":"dcf9e942bf197085ad98e5e43b3785bc10bafac4","tid":374950,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:56:53.000Z","msg":"因為中華地區傳統上黃色象徵高貴, 天子, 所以呢個文化既人好欣然接受西方人話佢地黃皮膚<br />\n但反之日本就視之為侮辱"},{"pid":"e50def21194aeb08a2eb3741af4aa39cb6fa255e","tid":374950,"uid":45914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:58:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a8859e8c0d93f8d4340d2b2b993eea2ef4028e2","tid":374950,"uid":122892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:59:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7fbedded03cc0137559e2671a4a903c16ceba46","tid":374950,"uid":55290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算，係有班傻仔自稱黃種人，咁撚黃去睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪就係，有病先係黃色皮膚。"},{"pid":"b243eac6ce6cd0ec32e10e1b0f15b0f3584a5c34","tid":374950,"uid":122892,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ab1feedad1e8a846328bdbc6204a38f0644163f","tid":374950,"uid":46151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/y3Ilc6T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fy3Ilc6T.jpg&h=2c3dff47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d04f5f9afeec5e078fff5db17b46020abbdad99","tid":374950,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:13:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔算，因為有牛肺</blockquote><br />\n依度我又想問多一個問題<br />\n如果毛髮顏色同黑色素有關<br />\n咁又點解我地係黑眼黑髮?<br />\n觀察上我諗的確係冇人會反對白人一定白過我地<br />\n點解有D金髮藍眼既白人就算冇曬黑，都係同我地一樣咁既色?<br />\n但我地從來唔會有D好白既人係金髮藍眼?</blockquote><br />\n可能頭髮同眼既黑色素未必係主因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東亞人都有好多係褐色，鬼佬隻眼都有幾隻色"},{"pid":"ab4c2a8b0f8160ba4fc6e1753c32492f41cf95ff","tid":374950,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但大陸農民果d皮膚真係好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔同香港人曬黑果隻黑，<br />\n真係紅蘿蔔一樣色<br />\n大陸大城市果d後生女都好白，但大媽係紅蘿蔔色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢大媽阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35c2576aa106bb83b059481c508a8539c0f0c42","tid":374950,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691afeee241b6146953cd681f755fef9909a0c10","tid":374950,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/y3Ilc6T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fy3Ilc6T.jpg&h=2c3dff47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nimmunoglobulin allotype根本唔可以correspond到去一個特定嘅膚色/種族<br />\n呢啲毫無根據嘅圖睇下就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}